Things I have done
* Created a login page , Forgot password page and Register page in ejs
* Forgot password sends a link for password change
* Created backend for this using NodeJS, MongoDB, Express, PassportJS 
* User invite using Nodemailer and redirect to register page
* Creation of group 
* Group chat and Private chat using socket rooms
* Friend requests using Nodemailer (accept and reject)
* Search using username using socket and see delivery status with time of delivery.
* Deletion of already sent messages.
* Send images as base64 string 